Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰頭地點是維尼特糰子店前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納 你到底打算睡到幾時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:29.10,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}追憶の扉を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:34.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}聞いていた音は囁き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:40.83,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}導いて魂の輪廻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.09,0:01:46.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一片の光の道へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:50.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}貫く痛みはInnocentre
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:55.08,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}信じたいよ 孤独じゃないこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:02:00.75,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}ここは彷徨いParadise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:06.53,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}白く心染める翼で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:13.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}もし君の瞳に 辿り着けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:16.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}笑って 抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:22.80,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}生まれてきた意味を知れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:26.36,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}見つめ合って 始まるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:30.37,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}Destiny in a jail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}王宮內 機關宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧克前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.97,0:02:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可隊長似乎從昨天起就沒回過房間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私自外宿？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 隊長一定不會做那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧克前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定隊長她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有什麼線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她或許和萊納·琉特在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}殲滅眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行的 請您站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能佩劍進去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在抱歉 我努力阻攔了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 她是我的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？陛下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 艾絲莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 你退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想當我的護衛去艾斯塔布爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們倆計劃逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 萊納卻沒出現在約定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是也想逃離和你的糰子之旅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有沒有什麼奇怪的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 昨天他好像見過我兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見過露西爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡之前 我回了趟宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為萊納說不定會在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他為何要去見露西爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長也不肯告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和萊納之間發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納…消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幫我背糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我說好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真的 大美人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩大人快介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有事要報告陛下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布爾的克拉烏前輩發來了報告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉烏髮來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯塔布爾出現了複寫眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎造成了相當大的損害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉烏率領羅蘭德軍和艾斯塔布爾軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往討伐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成…是萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納失蹤是在今晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方是複寫眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉烏前輩也沒那麼容易對付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要前往艾斯塔布爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援克拉烏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名複寫眼持有者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也必須秘密保護起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是詳細瞭解複寫眼的難得機會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲 搜索萊納的事交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以自由使喚這兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}舊艾斯塔布爾領內 森林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是複寫眼持有者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕無差錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時常進入我的領地 襲擊領民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑髮 黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑瞳中閃耀的紅色紋樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這複寫眼的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誆騙我們公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取我們國家的羅蘭德帝國元帥之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我好好見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑髮 黑衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑瞳中閃耀的紅色紋樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 看起來真是美味無比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複寫眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克帝國首都 格連斯雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣小小一個村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是連北方大陸最強大的史特歐爾公國
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是其手下敗將的國家的首都？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有吃人妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大肆破壞的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者末裔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡滿是神話傳說的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個奇怪的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧如此 我終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世界上有些人擁有人稱「魔眼」的特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人視能力不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼中有不同的紋樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以窺視別人夢境的「夢置眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吞噬人命的「殲滅眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說能解讀所有魔法的「複寫眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外還有「未來眼」「怨嗟眼」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前已確認的就是這五種
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複寫眼持有者出生時和人類的小孩沒有區別
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說其雙眼只需一掃就能識破世界的真理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解讀空氣中擴散的結構
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間理解魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 還會因某種契機而發狂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:09:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理崩潰 企圖抹消所有結構
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複寫眼持有者一旦發狂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法再恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納恢復原狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說萊納不是複寫眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩潰的黑之勇者 害怕寂寞的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 真是熱愛學習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷法爾·埃迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如休息一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.73,0:09:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒有香醇的茶水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這國王在這裡有什麼好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬琺·諾爾茲二等兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的女人的名字 當然會想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你調查過我的事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光查名字有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是追你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部下說想查你的生平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我讓他們別查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追女孩的時候不正面突破就沒意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我為什麼要來你這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是別國的間諜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自信還是有點看女人的眼光的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且同為痛恨戰爭的白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我們合得來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上哪有人會喜歡戰爭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也痛恨戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這個國家有你想知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始光是利用一下也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用我 利用這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這期間我一定會讓你愛上我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先給我喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,0)}{\fs40}舊艾斯塔布爾領內 貝爾特村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下 請看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了 終於
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個人的身體都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排好陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大規模魔法 準備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那傢伙 給我幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真是脆弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 用餐完畢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要退縮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須去找人才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩護閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人類來說真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神十足的肉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 成長得好美味的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天你沒殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡後悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元帥閣下 能打贏複寫眼怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然以人類來說 很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾獻上契約之文 將舞於天空的光之魔獸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為同伴報仇 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死的 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將其釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元帥閣下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅指克拉烏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 鎮定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下 您沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時沒下手真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 力量噴湧而出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下 這下我難保不將這裡的所有人殺個精光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要勉強了 閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.26,0:16:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是暫時撤退 先行治療…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傷勢反正逃不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來擋住那怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁此機會你帶軍隊撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽的話你也沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.26,0:16:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我給席恩和諾婭帶個好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要幫你跟公主殿下傳話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 你…快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睜開眼看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓克拉烏元帥閣下安全撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙…一群蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們羅蘭德的人都是蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是蠢得無藥可救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 只好幫你們一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫他們羅蘭德的蠢貨一把
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大規模魔法發射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會把同伴都捲進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙應該會吸收魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣能拖延時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧克前輩 做了很美味的蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快出來吧 蜜爾可隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納·琉特今晨離開了旅店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蜜爾可隊長到訪之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封命令書
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許給他看是個錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你們藏在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你們找我究竟有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可·卡拉德人在我們手上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.09,0:18:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我們走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盧克·斯塔卡德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我拒絕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可·卡拉德就沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得萊納·琉特把隊長帶走不大對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虜走隊長的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而目標是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉哩吧嗦什麼呢 還不乖乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 這是魔法陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 請別亂動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要動一下腳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.76,0:19:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會消失得連根指頭也不剩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想讓同為羅蘭德服務的人們喪命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你們的動作就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是在羅蘭德受過武術訓練的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而說到擁有像你這樣的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會綁架蜜爾可·卡拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又找我有事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭·弗洛瓦德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事早調查清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛瓦德大人 實在抱…歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是米蘭·弗洛瓦德中將嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 盧克·斯塔卡德中士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的強大我很清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二場戰役無敗績
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全都是在難以形容的劣勢情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你查得很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本所有戰役中我都沒用真名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的對手 似乎連小試牛刀也算不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可隊長在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事想請你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如陛下之命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你殺掉萊納·琉特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影 現形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗影…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.73,0:21:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你再動一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指和腦袋都會分家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好幫她背糰子的來著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.97,0:21:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉絲那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:04.84,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}忘れてたあの日の面影が
